Package org.cst8288Lab2.services

Class DataCSVProcessor

java.lang.Object
org.cst8288Lab2.services.CSVProcessor
org.cst8288Lab2.services.DataCSVProcessor
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileProcessor
public class DataCSVProcessor extends CSVProcessor
Extends CSVProcessor to specifically handle the processing of CSV files related to student and course data. It validates and persists student, course, and student-course relationships from the CSV data to the database and generates reports on the process.
